                        "text": "Have you been to Whitby Abbey? \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7 \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642\ufe0f \n\nIt\u2019s an incredible UK landmark located on the Yorkshire Coast \ud83d\udccd \n\nThe atmosphere there is undeniable, with a history dating back to 657AD \ud83d\ude2f which is only increased with its connection with Dracula \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642\ufe0f \n\nIn 1890 Bram Stoker sat overlooking the Abbey ruins and it was their gothic charm that assisted his inspiration for the world-famous novel, Dracula \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642\ufe0f \n\nAre you adding Whitby Abbey to your bucket list!? \u2728\n\n#whitby #visityorkshire #visitwhitby #whitbyabbey #visitengland #thisprettyengland #travelengland #uktravel #traveluk #uktravels #uktraveller #uktrip #travelbucketlist #travelreel"
